BEYOND the DARKNESS goes to the Down UnderWorld of the Paranormal in Australia with Anne Rzechowicz.

We try to avoid all the living things that want to kill you in Australia and make communication with the Undead of the Quarantine Station and other haunted habitats PLUS a NEW Theater of the Mind story from Melbourne, Australia.
